      "id": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/810620412714254336",
      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/810620412714254336",
      "title": "my books cartoon for this week&rsquo;s Guardian Books.",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/fd7f5cbd0cdfa485a3ed12bc47a2f75a/ede2565c4725b1bb-29/s640x960/656bba27b8740186692434a178835c2e95f18a1f.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"704\" data-orig-width=\"1200\" alt=\"&#10;&#10;&#10;Title: &quot;The Haters&quot;&#10;&#10;panel 1.&#10;Two round characters sit in a cinema.&#10;Yellow blob &quot;I hate this!&quot;&#10;Red Blob &quot;Me too!&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 2.&#10;They have left the cinema&#10;Red blob &quot;I hated every minute of that film! It was nothing like the book!&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 3.&#10;&quot;Did you like the book?&quot; asks Yellow.&#10;Red replies &quot;I hated it!&quot; then asks &quot;You?&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 4.&#10;Yellow blob &quot;I've not read it. I hated the film purely on its own merits.&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 5.&#10;Red blob &quot;I'll lend you my copy.&quot;&#10;Yello blob&quot;That's very kind.&quot;&#10;&#10;Panel 6.&#10;Caption: &quot;Later&quot;&#10;Yellow, reading the book &quot;I hate this!&quot;&#10;Red (happily) &quot;I knew you would!!&quot;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/fd7f5cbd0cdfa485a3ed12bc47a2f75a/ede2565c4725b1bb-29/s75x75_c1/1326d4636713ba6f3fc440f8ddfeecf6b9856bdd.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/fd7f5cbd0cdfa485a3ed12bc47a2f75a/ede2565c4725b1bb-29/s100x200/17c3ef8db89225b9aa43486c35c48de83e336161.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/fd7f5cbd0cdfa485a3ed12bc47a2f75a/ede2565c4725b1bb-29/s250x400/042dd038fd2e9198036dff1570c8005f6a21d6f9.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/fd7f5cbd0cdfa485a3ed12bc47a2f75a/ede2565c4725b1bb-29/s400x600/f570d9373273a6106942337f41d7d591b62f021a.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/fd7f5cbd0cdfa485a3ed12bc47a2f75a/ede2565c4725b1bb-29/s500x750/15bb7834f35aaf3dc7c790e669bd018b90792200.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/fd7f5cbd0cdfa485a3ed12bc47a2f75a/ede2565c4725b1bb-29/s540x810/9d45e221eb6043d0e40687c2941fee115d75e4f8.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/fd7f5cbd0cdfa485a3ed12bc47a2f75a/ede2565c4725b1bb-29/s640x960/656bba27b8740186692434a178835c2e95f18a1f.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/fd7f5cbd0cdfa485a3ed12bc47a2f75a/ede2565c4725b1bb-29/s1280x1920/5989c2abc96ee7f3e31dde8596df9868809c8156.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"/>"
