      "url": "https://myjetpack.tumblr.com/post/810176268616220672",
      "title": "A cartoon reminder that tomorrow is World Book Day (In the UK anyway). Originally for Guardian&hellip;",
      "content_html": "<img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/367b47aeb82492ca58546778565f7eee/8456ef593d701a01-7c/s640x960/c26e81f4897f18d801cb1bd25173774081559f32.jpg\" data-orig-height=\"532\" data-orig-width=\"960\" alt=\"A small girl wearing a rabbit costume and blue coat carries a book as she walks to school. &#10;&#10;Her mother (head out of shot) wheels her baby brother along in a pushchair. &#10;&#10;The baby says &quot;Peter Rabbit may be the 'Hero' of the story, but surely the obedient, widowed Mrs Rabbit is a more effective symbol of the oppression inherent within Mister McGregor's regime&quot;&#10;&#10;The girls looks furious and snaps &quot;Mum!! He's critiquing my world book day costume from a marxist perspective again!&quot;\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/367b47aeb82492ca58546778565f7eee/8456ef593d701a01-7c/s75x75_c1/fa223b9dba0020f1d991ed298a699128531deff7.jpg 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/367b47aeb82492ca58546778565f7eee/8456ef593d701a01-7c/s100x200/581ad01077551e41f6e52ea3374b727e3035fb09.jpg 100w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/367b47aeb82492ca58546778565f7eee/8456ef593d701a01-7c/s250x400/922b74ab3cd1eba53436118aa3d9ae6eaf46cc18.jpg 250w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/367b47aeb82492ca58546778565f7eee/8456ef593d701a01-7c/s400x600/c89cf302cc900ccc004f5b791c322ae670039cf9.jpg 400w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/367b47aeb82492ca58546778565f7eee/8456ef593d701a01-7c/s500x750/eb4de4abddb98df01f80a9c6327262276c637643.jpg 500w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/367b47aeb82492ca58546778565f7eee/8456ef593d701a01-7c/s540x810/4122564269a713290844fcf2cb8f41a98d3c0b3b.jpg 540w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/367b47aeb82492ca58546778565f7eee/8456ef593d701a01-7c/s640x960/c26e81f4897f18d801cb1bd25173774081559f32.jpg 640w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/367b47aeb82492ca58546778565f7eee/8456ef593d701a01-7c/s1280x1920/d001e1fdd09e1926386dc9930265d284a5072230.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"/>"
